column5: A tomestone containing data on Unei. Read the data with the demiclone generator to enable the creation of an Unei demiclone.
A tomestone containing data on Doga. Read the data with the demiclone generator to enable the creation of a Doga demiclone.
A tomestone containing data on onion knights. Read the data with the demiclone generator to enable the creation of an onion knight demiclone.
Juniper incense burned by the deceased in accordance with First Light funereal practices. Summons the faerie king to illuminate the path ahead.
Juniper incense burned by the deceased in accordance with First Light funereal practices. Summons the faerie king for a blessing of rejuvenation.
